To play Alc 2, follow the following steps:

1. Run the game through alc/Main.java
2. Click and drag the elements towards the middle of the screen
3. Place one element on top of another to combine them, if possible
4. Try to make the yellow potion!
5. To delete a unit, drag it into the brown "trash" square
5. At any time, scroll to zoom in/out, WASD to pan